cs.CL, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.NE, cs.DL 

This paper involves natural language processing and machine learning techniques to generate classical Chinese poems from vernacular Chinese. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.CL (Computation and Language). Additionally, the paper uses unsupervised machine translation, which falls under the sub-categories of cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.LG (Learning). The paper also uses reinforcement learning, which is a sub-category of cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing). Finally, the paper involves deep learning techniques, which falls under the sub-category of cs.DL (Machine Learning).
